ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我出翻去先<br />\n我睇左做好大便嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打少啲飛機啦巴打"},{"pid":"4f783cc3dea95a06d1dfa743d1d54f55f631d137","tid":315590,"uid":71694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"有錢人食大家樂大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282ec5f6c5fc50a1a01519658f074c9979f6552e","tid":315590,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb723f0bdbf3ad038e790a7eb98d96d7aa968f3f","tid":315590,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係香港, 有$在全世界都係天堂, 冇$處處都在地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c809910449da93db588cfe5131a1e647272712a","tid":315590,"uid":71694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有錢人食大家樂大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到呢度眼都突埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友將自己食開嘅代入埋有錢人度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a641fa766b163354aaf0437c347809dacf0c8f","tid":315590,"uid":71740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"大家樂大快樂係d低產，廢青，新移民先吃架炸，中產都唔會吃呢d低質垃圾，咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：低產廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc20a5f37a4f560392dc9bd6290384ca9ca3c383"